text: Mock Up on Mu is a 2008 science fiction collage film. It was directed by American experimental filmmaker Craig Baldwin. The film develops a fictionalized continuation of the story of L. Ron Hubbard, Jack Parsons, and Marjorie Cameron. Baldwin assembled it mostly from found footage but began introducing more original live-action footage than in earlier projects. == Cast == * Damon Packard as L. Ron Hubbard * Kal Spelletich as Jack Parsons * Michelle Silva as Marjorie Cameron * Stoney Burke as Lockheed Martin == Release == Mock Up on Mu first appearedd at the 2008 San Francisco International Film Festival. Later, it was released at the New York Film Festival in 2008. == References == == Other websites == * Mock Up on Mu at Other Cinema * * * Category:2000s English-language movies Category:American science fiction movies Category:2008 movies Category:2000s science fiction movies
